"Universal Link Protection:" = "Universal Link保護:";

"Use when you need to evade censorship and prevent someone from monitoring your activity, but are less concerned about leakage of your identity to adversaries." = "活動を監視・検閲されることを避ける必要があるが、身元についてはそれほど神経質ではない場合。";

